## 可访问性

### ARIA 属性

```tsx
<button
  aria-label="关闭对话框"
  aria-expanded={isOpen}
  onClick={handleClose}
>
  <XIcon />
</button>
```

### 键盘导航

```tsx
<div
  role="button"
  tabIndex={0}
  onKeyDown={(e) => {
    if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') {
      handleClick();
    }
  }}
>
  Click me
</div>
```

